Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}名为α的野兽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.65,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样擅自行动可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你会来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉拉·琉特鲁公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是长大了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔·艾利斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在还不到可以看「门」的阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是由你来决定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您果然是个阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜这个是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者遗物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西可是杀不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧 神兽灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次见面之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到可以杀死你的咒语才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉特鲁公爵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么没杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那口气 倒是越来越像样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉拉·琉特鲁公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那侵蚀罗兰德的该死亡灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界似乎起了巨大的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是我理想中的王者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切遵照您的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救…这腐朽的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天叫你来不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想知道你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不满意你的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就听听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问吧 露西尔·艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再驻足不前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻挡在眼前的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁都杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我什么都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直 一直在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 成为吾主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切献作祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为吾剑之主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将是吞噬 开拓这世界的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 拯救世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将消失的假货还能有合作为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说八道 你才是假货
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你会输
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不认为那笨蛋轻易就会死…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有美丽的小姐跟我搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 到底对莱纳做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢莱纳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有一套嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还真想多看看你的真本领
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若敢小看我 小心没命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会没命？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重量大概三倍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想了 你没有胜算的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你问我对莱纳做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用小刀插进他的心脏杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他血流如注 表情甚是可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳死了 你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 惹哭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉这么欺负你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如此重视莱纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起源（α）即破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾不行创造
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行惠泽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅行消除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归纯白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天吾等了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟以为这种仿冒品就能封住吾等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬了你 便能解除这封印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾将前往「α」 一切遵照契约
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 解开所有公式者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体实验？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有报告说其发狂后从实验设施逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个破忌者　因为被施过禁忌之术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得了超越常人的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀 杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 阿斯塔尔陛下即位以来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体实验应该被禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是罗兰德帝国破忌者追击部队队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜尔可·卡拉德中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你习得了罗兰德魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上头有令 那个破忌者杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下知道这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 因为人体实验是陛下的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下他…正常吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 无比正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为有必要才重新开始这种实验
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:12:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…卢克你们一直瞒着我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗兰德的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以…解脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了…就能解脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以活着长大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会和我结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果幸存下来 能和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算约定…也没有意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是要死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 太爱哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说什么要死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的啦 这么顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也没打算死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你也别死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能救你 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能这样做 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使接下来即将发生一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在陛下的剧本之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所生存的国度 我一定会守护到底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 阿特法尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的诅咒就想压制我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你长得…这么大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉拉 是你给了我时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为了见你 一直在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了…见我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你 莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「编造所有公式者」出现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快往深处去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去触碰「门」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了守护你珍重的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区一个祭品 大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆大胆大胆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再多碰碰你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多说几声我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想一直陪在你身边 看着你成长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要我做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要在此成为吾之祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救…我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…将你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是突然被奇怪的家伙捅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是逃避的你 无法拯救莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以拯救世界为借口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出卖了莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要闭嘴的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别满口空想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避选择 逃避恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避痛苦的你救不了莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不让你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就从黑暗中拯救莱纳看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你做得到 我早就做了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我还是要救莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会杀了莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他陷入黑暗之前救他出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要睡着就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会终结一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 到底谁赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了吧 要怎么处置莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 你也不记得发生了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像有人告诉了我什么很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:31.43,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}忘れてたあの日の面影が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:31.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}那一天已忘却的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:37.39,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}空の向こう 微かに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:37.39,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}在天空彼方隐隐浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:45.47,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心なら繋がっていたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:45.47,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心灵原本应早已相通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:52.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}震えた瞳は応えずに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:52.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}颤抖的瞳眸却无回应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:56.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに信じても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:56.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}如何相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:59.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに伝えたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:59.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}如何呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:05.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}この声は届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:05.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}这声音你已无法听到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:10.77,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}光のフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:10.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}光之Fillment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:15.63,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}全てをこの身体に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:15.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一一铭刻于此身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:20.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}歩き出す ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:20.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}就从此地 迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:24.42,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}記憶のセグメント
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:24.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}记忆的Segment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:29.76,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}今絡まる運命の糸解き
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:29.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}解开此刻交缠的命运丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:33.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}強くなりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:33.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:36.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}また出逢えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:36.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}若能再重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:46.25,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}もっと守れるように 君を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:46.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}定能守护你 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开所有公式者…是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你竟然查到这么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我看中的人 果然优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在罗兰德发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有其真正意义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会这么拼命 是为了莱纳·琉特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救世界而奋战不休的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩溃以后追求力量 最终被封印起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而为了解除这封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬了害怕寂寞的恶魔之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕寂寞的恶魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克很快就将进攻中央大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会和罗兰德正面冲突吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 我要借你之手救出莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在席恩·阿斯塔尔背叛莱纳之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩怎么会背叛莱纳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堕落的黑暗勇者为了拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将吞噬害怕寂寞的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比死更残酷的绝望 吞噬莱纳·琉特之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把他救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从堕落的黑暗勇者手中救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要带着莱纳回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单恋真痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 一切准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要向未来前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让不再有泪水的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:23:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱纳…
